Pre-Game Insights: Hong Kong and Kuwait will lock horns in the 21st T20I of ICC Mens T20 World Cup Asia Qualifier A 2024 on Monday, 9 September 2024, at UKM-YSD Cricket Oval, Bangi.
In Match 18 of the ICC Men’s T20 World Cup Asia Sub-Regional Qualifier A, Malaysia narrowly defeated Hong Kong by 3 runs.
In Match 17 of the ICC Men’s T20 World Cup Asia Sub-Regional Qualifier A, the Maldives defeated Mongolia by 117 runs.
